column1: Elizabeth Warren asks: “what has the Covid virus done to our babies?” Why isn’t she asking what has abortion done to our babies? Especially black babies? Black lives do matter. Black babies lives matter also. Such hypocrisy! Thank GOD for a Pro-Life Donald Trump! @realDonaldTrump

This morning @USDOL launched an interactive online tool to assist workers in determining paid sick leave or extended family+medical leave eligibility pursuant to the Families First Coronavirus Response Act (FFCRA).  Link: https://t.co/jgUrR1v81V

Expanded testing in rural areas—This week @HHSGov announced that #Texas 303 Rural Health Clinics will receive ~$50000 each to be used for #COVID19 testing and other expenses incl. training staff on testing procedures & data reporting to HHS. Good news!
